in there just in case

00:01:18.030 --> 00:01:19.738 align:middle line:84%
because there's nothing
worse than having

00:01:19.738 --> 00:01:23.270 align:middle line:84%
a creamy sauce with a bit of
grit when you're eating it.

00:01:23.270 --> 00:01:25.720 align:middle line:84%
