well, as you can see,

00:01:25.720 --> 00:01:28.580 align:middle line:84%
and just making sure I
haven't left anything

00:01:28.580 --> 00:01:31.480 align:middle line:90%
in between the actual leaves.

00:01:31.480 --> 00:01:36.020 align:middle line:84%
