this about 10 minutes.

00:02:59.288 --> 00:03:01.510 align:middle line:84%
OK, so this has
come up to the boil.

00:03:01.510 --> 00:03:03.820 align:middle line:84%
And a really,
really good tip here

00:03:03.820 --> 00:03:07.480 align:middle line:84%
is to skim the
impurities off the top.

00:03:07.480 --> 00:03:09.170 align:middle line:90%
