it's just going to explode.

00:03:41.650 --> 00:03:42.450 align:middle line:90%
OK?

00:03:42.450 --> 00:03:44.242 align:middle line:84%
So it's really important,
so take your time

00:03:44.242 --> 00:03:46.090 align:middle line:84%
with this if you're
not used to doing this.

00:03:46.090 --> 00:03:48.600 align:middle line:84%
So I've got my ladle
and my blender,

00:03:48.600 --> 00:03:51.250 align:middle line:84%
